{"title":"Far Inhibidores de la enzima dipeptidilpeptidasa 4 (iDPP-4)","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Far Inhibidores de la enzima dipeptidilpeptidasa 4 (iDPP-4)-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Inhibidores de la enzima\\Ndipeptidil peptidasa 4 (iDPP-4)","guid":"vZzcMqVnbnMi6EuhvaTSUg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Función de las incretinas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Hormonas intestinales → secreción por ingesta de nutrientes","guid":"ezxFwCX1_IR2DTWetZ3qVg","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Estimulan secreción de insulina (glucosa-dependiente)","guid":"5rRVB0Th5umpiKlivhT2hQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Reducen concentración de glucagón (1)","guid":"5Yx29rz6uzhkbbHVK8oslw","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"Mecanismo de\\Nacción de iDPP-4:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Inhiben enzima que degrada incretinas","guid":"sx_ChxQ-LQaTvoBqHh_PSg","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• ↑ Niveles de GLP-1 y otras hormonas incretinas","guid":"pkvpTQWRCohvYMf2tXpYXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Efectos clínicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Reducción moderada de A1c","guid":"E7Zn0r_VtrPzdKH4YBnOSg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"• Fármacos neutros en peso","guid":"m1duOxPcitzgy89CevtayA","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"• Rara asociación a hipoglicemia (2)","guid":"mDuReane881HKKQdnfArPw","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"Seguridad\\Ncardiovascular:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• No ↑ riesgo de eventos cardiovasculares ateroescleróticos","guid":"jMFtWh-g1NXMupE4cbh64A","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Saxagliptina asociada a descompensación de insuficiencia\\Ncardíaca en pacientes con esta condición (3)","guid":"-QIA8cX7z2F1euxjZSnepw","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"0","text":"Metabolismo y\\Ndosificación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• Metabolismo renal (excepto linagliptina) → ajustar dosificación según función renal","guid":"c49DGEK4nD3kGdJ5vWteVA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"• Vildagliptina: no usar en insuficiencia hepática o ↑ transaminasas > 2,5x valor ref","guid":"-d6qfcCnT5_aj0f-M2W4Fw","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"Precauciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Descontinuar en caso de pancreatitis","guid":"BZqnmmSVa2aZj0bm8kUAgg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• Advertencia: artralgias graves y penfigoide buloso (4)","guid":"5P8EKtZtgQkapEvaUL0KXg","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Asociación con\\Notros fármacos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Asociable con otros antidiabéticos orales e insulina","guid":"i6paRLnOXSI8GO8GbVc5eQ","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• Presentaciones combinadas con metformina disponibles","guid":"Vr8JfaOfv7vXA2V1ROS-EQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"• No usar con arGLP-1 (5)","guid":"VcJEIFpuEss8HezFxWK5Mg","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"Características\\Nde los iDPP-4","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"1. Linagliptina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Formulación: 5 mg","guid":"zAmVlIAYdnUfoPxRoOoK2Q","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Dosis diaria: 5 mg","guid":"ZHWTnhyGUS7t9FIY9gOE5g","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Uso en insuficiencia renal: No requiere ajuste","guid":"PgByO12NC32XDed0WiFS2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"25","text":"2. Saxagliptina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Formulación: 5 mg","guid":"9uV4ftRzcsui_OxoRbdN1A","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• Dosis diaria: 2.5 a 5 mg","guid":"kBYPOZYs44CManWUd3eRaQ","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"• Uso en insuficiencia renal: Ajustar si VFG ≤ 50 mL/min o diálisis","guid":"lzBanCmwWU_vdxpwG3YS4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"25","text":"3. Sitagliptina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Formulación: 100 mg","guid":"KK8fMpeGkB8p-qpdYhzXkw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Dosis diaria: 100 mg","guid":"xdU_Rmq0_Q455aMbP-8I1A","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"• Uso en\\Ninsuficiencia renal:","guid":"zWpYvMjdSbWP2BRK_AxSUA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Ajustar si VFG < 30 a ≤ 50 mL/min a 50 mg","guid":"DsO649jIEWKDmTcK7AzxrQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Ajustar si VFG < 30 mL/min o diálisis a 25 mg","guid":"MwFiwBk2JvWuaSUPMODn3w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"25","text":"4. Vildagliptina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Formulación: 50 mg","guid":"0qT8voRD8XcM97Iov52ovw","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"• Dosis diaria: 50 a 100 mg","guid":"BZ0YgT8GkMZUvkXCUPb1NQ","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"• Uso en insuficiencia renal: Ajustar si VFG\\N≤ 50 mL/min o diálisis a 50 mg","guid":"ciuBdfgLIfO8j-bH30gi7A","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":43,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Far Inhibidores de la enzima dipeptidilpeptidasa 4 (iDPP-4)-2024","id":"map_757","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Far Inhibidores de la enzima dipeptidilpeptidasa 4 (iDPP-4)-2024"}